        ------
        - Mouse scrolling support (thanks to Wes Turner)
        - Bugfix: Escape HTML entities without borking tweet text (thanks to David Tiersch)
        
        0.2.19
        ------
        - Bugfix: Restore Python 2.6 compatibility
        
        0.2.18
